# EdgeSOM - Full-Stack AI Solutions: From Training to Mass Production

> EdgeSOM is a premier provider of integrated AI solutions, bridging the gap between AI model training and physical hardware mass production for toys, companion robots, and smart home systems.

## Specialized AI Solutions
- **AI Toy Solutions**: Interactive hardware scaling for smart, educational, and fun AI-driven toys.
- **AI Companion Robotics**: Development of social and emotional support companion robots from concept to reality.
- **AI Smart Home Solutions**: IoT integration and mass production for intelligent home ecosystems.
- **AI Education Solutions**: Smart learning hardware designed for the next generation of STEM.

## Core Technical Capabilities
- **LLM Training & Model Distillation**: Expertise in training large language models and distilling them for efficient edge device deployment.
- **End-to-End Production**: Complete workflow from R&D and PCBA design to ISO-certified mass production.
- **Embedded Integration**: Seamlessly embedding sophisticated AI algorithms into cost-effective hardware modules.

